{"tid":1424647,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"司長話暴力之下唔回應，當初和平示威又有回應咩？？","createTime":"2019-08-06T16:16:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T17:07:13.000Z","uid":276720,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0546cb783e5b65986c4c4177f1267c60e43b65ff","tid":1424647,"uid":276720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:16:01.000Z","msg":"容小弟有感而發（有啲長&hellip;sorry哂）<br />\n<br />\n今日放工特登去聽政府回應不合作運動，聽到張建宗係咁講暴力示威衝突之下，首要係停止暴力，唔安全社會氣氛下冇條件傾。幾多萬人上街行冇問題架&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\nDLLM啦，你就梗係冇問題啦，仲懶得理你添啦。你唔諗下點解場運動會由<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和平示威集會遊行</span></span></span></span></span>演變到<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警民衝突，罷工</span></span>？？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係因為和平理性政府唔理呀</span></span><br />\n<br />\n由一開始律師們最早發聲反對，到幾十萬人上街，100萬人上街，和平之下有咩結果？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府無視民意，強推二讀!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以小弟覺得記者可以問一問：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">政府係示威者和平表演訴求果陣<span style=\"color: red;\">全不回應</span>，點解依加仲叫示威者唔升級行動，和平表達？</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家都太著眼係衝突上，事出有因，我以上所講嘅就係&ldquo;因&rdquo;。而最初就係因為政府唔回應，同埋唔肯用&ldquo;撤回&rdquo;二字。班狗官仲問示威者點解仲提反修例，都壽終正寢咗啦。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係因為&ldquo;撤回&rdquo;二字先有法律效力呀</span></span><br />\n既然狗官扮聽唔到，係加又日日有記召，就當面問多佢一次啦唔該。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">政府到幾時先肯用&ldquo;撤回&rdquo;呢個具法律效力嘅字眼，而唔係其他任何詞語去&ldquo;正正式式&rdquo; &ldquo;撤回&rdquo;結束修例工作。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n另外政府唔肯一次過答你5大訴求，唔清唔楚，佢地想唔知5大係邊5大咁。有冇得逐個訴求一條條咁當面問？<br />\n<br />\n當然其他一大堆比卡超唔回應警黑呀，委任證呀，TG射800粒合唔合理呀，射民居，過期之類大家有討論開我就唔係呢個post到再提啦。<br />\n<br />\n香港今次唔輸得！！"},{"pid":"23115663c3b15af37d88c505a7f624cb81d2a30b","tid":1424647,"uid":276720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:19:44.000Z","msg":"自推理性討論"},{"pid":"cc7dadf68b6bce444d484734f0d6676825f36608","tid":1424647,"uid":276720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:19:55.000Z","msg":"自推理性討論"},{"pid":"87f5de3e0b3134a92c62d0e9258699f2932d1d6f","tid":1424647,"uid":276720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:25:42.000Z","msg":"p牌仔冇人理唯有自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"766f6d6cf7bbd7bd450ba628eb5bd1dc2830e5da","tid":1424647,"uid":276720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:25:56.000Z","msg":"牌仔冇人理唯有自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e27b0d62a1d28c4b5f5235a1465fc0c741ef511c","tid":1424647,"uid":276720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:26:06.000Z","msg":"牌仔冇人理唯有自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e0cdad0800a354164cbca24aacf33d933e15299","tid":1424647,"uid":276720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:26:16.000Z","msg":"牌仔冇人理唯有自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b415179eabe07cc5962ac49b99e7966b783c28a","tid":1424647,"uid":276720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:26:39.000Z","msg":"p牌仔冇人理唯有自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ab95b3ebfac01e1ad15ff2e34291954c5422974","tid":1424647,"uid":60563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:33:10.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n可能呢度大家都明所以冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76dda20a21c1a7a80fcb1cf8f542ed1566895e2c","tid":1424647,"uid":276720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:07:13.000Z","msg":"真心覺得要正面直接問政府，冇得避<br />\n我知721大家好關注 但唔